WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: _P6vhwxRuts

NOTE Language: en

01:12:57.648 --> 01:13:03.098
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

01:13:09.059 --> 01:13:11.514
At the very outset,

01:13:11.542 --> 01:13:16.923
I have to tell you that Truth is what it is.

01:13:16.961 --> 01:13:19.409
You cannot change it,

01:13:19.450 --> 01:13:22.385
you cannot transform it,

01:13:22.389 --> 01:13:24.915
you cannot explain it.

01:13:24.940 --> 01:13:28.290
Only thing you can experience it.

01:13:31.245 --> 01:13:33.352
In this Kali Yuga

01:13:33.502 --> 01:13:37.643
there is a special category of people born

01:13:37.672 --> 01:13:40.673
in all the countries very surprisingly,

01:13:40.712 --> 01:13:44.438
who are seekers of Truth.

01:13:44.453 --> 01:13:51.414
And William Blake, the great poet of England

01:13:51.484 --> 01:13:53.734
has said that

01:13:55.073 --> 01:13:59.887
these men of God will be born during this time

01:13:59.938 --> 01:14:03.147
and they will know the truth

01:14:03.188 --> 01:14:05.418
So many have said about this.

01:14:05.445 --> 01:14:10.605
Even in our old books of prophecies.

01:14:13.114 --> 01:14:15.594
You have known so many of them

01:14:15.674 --> 01:14:19.442
but especially the one which is described

01:14:19.513 --> 01:14:23.007
in Nadi Granth written by Bhrigu Muni

01:14:23.088 --> 01:14:25.977
is clearly said that at this time

01:14:26.028 --> 01:14:30.882
people will know the Truth through the Kundalini Awakening.

01:14:30.903 --> 01:14:33.883
The knowledge of Kundalini was known to us,

01:14:33.933 --> 01:14:37.414
I don’t know how many years back.

01:14:37.504 --> 01:14:42.147
You cannot say because our history is so unknown.

01:14:42.203 --> 01:14:47.938
But at the time of a great saint

01:14:47.951 --> 01:14:51.389
called as Macchindra Nath and Gorakh Nath,

01:14:51.408 --> 01:14:55.700
they were indulging into

01:14:55.749 --> 01:14:58.816
awakening of Kundalini

01:14:58.865 --> 01:15:04.240
but the condition was that one Guru should give Realisation to only one person.

01:15:04.251 --> 01:15:06.361
Went on like this

01:15:06.370 --> 01:15:08.750
till the twelfth century when

01:15:08.758 --> 01:15:11.351
Gyandeva first of all asked his Guru,

01:15:11.358 --> 01:15:14.680
his own Master was his own brother.

01:15:14.678 --> 01:15:15.720
asked him that,

01:15:15.727 --> 01:15:20.869
“You please allow me to at least write about Kundalini.”

01:15:20.908 --> 01:15:25.956
Because in the Gita it was not described.

01:15:25.982 --> 01:15:29.546
Though Shri Krishna has talked of Sthit Pragnya and all those things

01:15:29.571 --> 01:15:33.112
but he didn’t talk about:

01:15:33.125 --> 01:15:34.131
How to get it?

01:15:34.160 --> 01:15:38.429
What is the mechanism within us which works it out?

01:15:38.489 --> 01:15:43.220
Then he wrote it in his Gyaneshwari

01:15:43.268 --> 01:15:46.018
which is just a, I think,

01:15:46.077 --> 01:15:48.797
explanation of Gita very clearly

01:15:48.868 --> 01:15:52.818
that there is a power within us.

01:15:54.088 --> 01:15:56.957
In the sixth chapter he wrote about Kundalini

01:15:57.218 --> 01:16:01.476
but the people who were in charge of religion didn’t want that.

01:16:01.501 --> 01:16:04.161
So they said, “This is a Nishiddha (prohibited) part

01:16:04.221 --> 01:16:07.523
and you should not read this part of Kundalini.”

01:16:07.531 --> 01:16:09.792
But in the sixteenth century

01:16:09.811 --> 01:16:12.619
under the guidance of Guru Nanaka,

01:16:12.660 --> 01:16:13.660
Namdeva,

01:16:13.690 --> 01:16:15.053
Kabira,

01:16:15.070 --> 01:16:21.555
all these people, clearly, clearly, very clearly wrote about Kundalini

01:16:21.601 --> 01:16:25.855
but the way it was mutilated

01:16:25.872 --> 01:16:28.918
by

01:16:28.939 --> 01:16:31.481
people which is very surprising.

01:16:31.499 --> 01:16:33.311
Everything has been mutilated

01:16:33.332 --> 01:16:36.055
but this one was very surprising

01:16:36.086 --> 01:16:39.985
because Kabira was in Bihar

01:16:39.994 --> 01:16:42.285
and he called Kundalini as Surti.

01:16:42.304 --> 01:16:44.885
Very clearly, he said about Surti

01:16:44.894 --> 01:16:50.834
but in Bihar, ‘Surti’ is what you call ‘tobacco’.

01:16:50.856 --> 01:16:52.614
They call ‘tobacco’ as ‘Surti’,

01:16:52.617 --> 01:16:55.690
so you can imagine what is the mutilation.

01:16:55.696 --> 01:16:58.887
Now this power is within you.

01:16:58.936 --> 01:17:00.787
If I am telling you something today

01:17:00.808 --> 01:17:02.588
you need not accept it.

01:17:02.628 --> 01:17:05.207
Blind folded acceptance is of no use.

01:17:05.237 --> 01:17:08.634
We have had enough problems with blind faiths.

01:17:08.648 --> 01:17:10.600
So, first of all

01:17:10.601 --> 01:17:12.170
you must get the experience

01:17:12.182 --> 01:17:16.004
and then you will not doubt it.

01:17:16.001 --> 01:17:19.848
This science was known to us since long

01:17:19.888 --> 01:17:22.208
but as it was only done for one person

01:17:22.237 --> 01:17:25.458
or say ten persons at the most,

01:17:25.468 --> 01:17:28.318
I decided to find out a method by which

01:17:28.348 --> 01:17:32.218
an en-masse Realisation could be given.

01:17:32.239 --> 01:17:35.110
Luckily my father was a very social person

01:17:35.189 --> 01:17:37.809
and I could meet many people.

01:17:37.860 --> 01:17:42.153
Even my husband’s life was such that I could meet many people.

01:17:42.203 --> 01:17:48.804
So, I worked out the permutations and combinations of human problems

01:17:48.855 --> 01:17:50.669
and then I discovered

01:17:50.715 --> 01:17:53.388
how we can easily solve this problem

01:17:53.405 --> 01:17:55.528
of Kundalini awakening.

01:17:55.516 --> 01:17:57.898
Because there are problems

01:17:57.936 --> 01:18:00.049
on the way of its ascent

01:18:00.091 --> 01:18:03.771
then Kundalini doesn’t, Kundalini doesn’t come up.

01:18:03.811 --> 01:18:05.340
Now

01:18:05.389 --> 01:18:07.829
there are seven chakras

01:18:07.891 --> 01:18:10.699
basically within us.

01:18:10.742 --> 01:18:13.826
These seven chakras are responsible

01:18:13.888 --> 01:18:18.484
of our physical, mental and emotional being.

01:18:18.497 --> 01:18:20.184
There is no doubt about it

01:18:20.198 --> 01:18:22.528
but you have to first find out

01:18:22.521 --> 01:18:23.614
and then believe in it.

01:18:23.634 --> 01:18:25.814
Don’t believe because I am saying so

01:18:25.835 --> 01:18:30.117
or anybody says so. You have to experience it and feel it.

01:18:30.124 --> 01:18:32.427
There are many ways we can also judge.

01:18:32.434 --> 01:18:34.927
For example,

01:18:34.948 --> 01:18:36.477
in the Koran,

01:18:36.487 --> 01:18:41.427
Mohammed Sahib has said, “At the time of Kayama, means this time of Resurrection,

01:18:41.468 --> 01:18:43.328
your hands will speak.”

01:18:43.367 --> 01:18:45.287
He also calls it ‘Kayamat’

01:18:45.331 --> 01:18:48.341
means ‘those who will not accept will suffer’.

01:18:48.362 --> 01:18:50.782
But who will accept their hands will speak,

01:18:50.802 --> 01:18:52.073
their

01:18:52.133 --> 01:18:54.773
mouth will be shut and their hands will speak?

01:18:54.843 --> 01:18:57.033
This is exactly what happens in Sahaja Yoga

01:18:57.112 --> 01:19:00.071
that once you get your Self-realisation

01:19:00.117 --> 01:19:03.521
you can feel those subtle centres within you.

01:19:03.557 --> 01:19:05.674
These subtle centres of energy

01:19:05.703 --> 01:19:07.393
are seven in number

01:19:07.417 --> 01:19:15.328
and are acting for giving us all kinds of energies.

01:19:15.377 --> 01:19:18.244
Now the problem is how to make

01:19:18.258 --> 01:19:20.114
people believe in Kundalini.

01:19:20.127 --> 01:19:22.014
It’s a difficult task

01:19:22.016 --> 01:19:23.905
because you are all intellectuals

01:19:23.917 --> 01:19:27.645
and you have had your medical education

01:19:27.657 --> 01:19:30.557
from England and all these places you see.

01:19:30.566 --> 01:19:32.287
It is more westernised

01:19:32.300 --> 01:19:34.562
and to believe in something Indian

01:19:34.600 --> 01:19:38.403
is rather difficult for people that it’s all Indian after all.

01:19:38.441 --> 01:19:41.550
But actually, even in medical science

01:19:41.621 --> 01:19:44.751
we have to understand the limitations of a science.

01:19:44.780 --> 01:19:49.059
First of all, science is amoral.

01:19:50.170 --> 01:19:53.412
Secondly, it does not go to the roots.

01:19:53.417 --> 01:19:57.782
So, it starts like we have to treat a tree.

01:19:57.787 --> 01:19:59.432
So, we treat the leaves,

01:19:59.448 --> 01:20:00.843
treat the branches

01:20:00.893 --> 01:20:03.182
but Sahaja Yoga is going to the roots,

01:20:03.223 --> 01:20:04.900
is the knowledge of the roots.

01:20:04.924 --> 01:20:09.888
And the roots are the seven chakras and our Kundalini.

01:20:10.188 --> 01:20:13.560
Of course, without medical science you cannot also understand Sahaja Yoga.

01:20:13.581 --> 01:20:19.714
That is also one of the things because you can relate very easily. It is very scientific.

01:20:19.730 --> 01:20:22.490
Now there are three Nadis also

01:20:22.541 --> 01:20:25.219
Left, Right and Centre.

01:20:25.240 --> 01:20:28.048
Left is called as Ida Nadi,

01:20:28.129 --> 01:20:29.848
right as Pingala

01:20:29.928 --> 01:20:36.959
and the central one is called as Sushumna Nadi.

01:20:40.677 --> 01:20:43.267
Kabira has described it very clearly

01:20:43.327 --> 01:20:46.213
and it is in the Granth Sahib

01:20:46.233 --> 01:20:49.783
written down but nobody tries to understand

01:20:49.824 --> 01:20:51.343
or to go beyond the words.

01:20:51.363 --> 01:20:54.513
Just go and read the words that is not going to help.

01:20:54.533 --> 01:20:55.943
You have to go beyond it.

01:20:55.945 --> 01:21:01.043
It is like this, you see a beautiful picture say where it’s raining,

01:21:01.074 --> 01:21:05.703
it’s very beautiful and you are seeing it, that’s all.

01:21:05.721 --> 01:21:09.209
But you are not inside it to experience it.

01:21:09.279 --> 01:21:11.829
So, to enter inside was difficult one

01:21:11.899 --> 01:21:15.411
because of the tradition of giving to one person only,

01:21:15.440 --> 01:21:16.889
or to few persons

01:21:16.899 --> 01:21:18.961
and secondly the greatest objection

01:21:18.971 --> 01:21:22.721
came from people, who were in charge of religion

01:21:22.740 --> 01:21:24.240
so called

01:21:24.265 --> 01:21:26.255
Nowadays those who are intellectuals,

01:21:26.276 --> 01:21:32.497
you should say medias and other people

01:21:32.526 --> 01:21:35.634
who have a feeling that they know everything,

01:21:35.643 --> 01:21:39.300
they don’t want to take anything, that is to begin with.

01:21:39.324 --> 01:21:41.401
This is one of the reasons why

01:21:41.416 --> 01:21:46.559
people don’t turn their eyes to the great knowledge we have in this country

01:21:46.576 --> 01:21:50.829
I am so very happy today that

01:21:50.847 --> 01:21:53.499
Indian Medical Association

01:21:53.526 --> 01:21:56.133
has given me this honour first of all

01:21:56.166 --> 01:21:59.478
because I could never imagine in my lifetime,

01:21:59.496 --> 01:22:01.553
I would be able to talk with you.

01:22:01.583 --> 01:22:06.037
I also did my medicine and I knew how difficult it was

01:22:06.070 --> 01:22:08.021
and how people were blind.

01:22:08.090 --> 01:22:11.417
So, I used to think, “How will I explain to them”,

01:22:11.458 --> 01:22:12.742
like Kabira has said,

01:22:12.741 --> 01:22:17.982
“Kaise samjhau, sab jag andha” (How to make them understand when the whole world is blind?)

01:22:18.006 --> 01:22:20.642
But the time has come because there are seekers now.

01:22:20.666 --> 01:22:22.811
And they should also know one more thing,

01:22:22.825 --> 01:22:25.252
that this country is the Yogabhoomi.

01:22:25.286 --> 01:22:27.291
They have given us science all right

01:22:27.328 --> 01:22:28.698
but we will give them Yoga.

01:22:28.747 --> 01:22:34.723
We will give them the real basic knowledge

01:22:34.753 --> 01:22:39.822
what is the foundation of Medical Science,

01:22:39.829 --> 01:22:41.849
is the foundation!

01:22:41.869 --> 01:22:46.049
Now by experimenting this and that

01:22:46.049 --> 01:22:49.526
also you have seen that it is neutralised by challenges.

01:22:49.541 --> 01:22:51.569
Every theory is neutralised

01:22:51.579 --> 01:22:54.214
so that means it is not Absolute.

01:22:54.241 --> 01:22:58.253
So, we have to go to something that is absolutely Absolute

01:22:58.291 --> 01:23:01.251
You have seen that Einstein found out something

01:23:01.300 --> 01:23:03.054
then our people are after him

01:23:03.080 --> 01:23:06.073
this is wrong, that is wrong, going on like that.

01:23:06.100 --> 01:23:09.543
All the time something comes up, people go on criticising

01:23:09.550 --> 01:23:14.155
and the whole knowledge goes into oblivion.

01:23:14.190 --> 01:23:19.015
So now we have to understand that if this is the Yogabhoomi,

01:23:19.335 --> 01:23:21.167
this is our country

01:23:21.187 --> 01:23:23.969
and if it has given us such a knowledge,

01:23:23.996 --> 01:23:27.267
why should we not also listen to it,

01:23:27.276 --> 01:23:32.772
because not only that it will flower your knowledge of medicine,

01:23:32.796 --> 01:23:39.537
not only that but it will give you such a confidence while practicing,

01:23:39.536 --> 01:23:42.313
while talking about medicine.

01:23:42.324 --> 01:23:45.523
Now as it is a subject,

01:23:45.544 --> 01:23:47.133
is on medicine

01:23:47.153 --> 01:23:50.147
I would like to speak on one of the centres

01:23:50.177 --> 01:23:54.824
which is very important because doctors are always affected by that centre.

01:23:54.840 --> 01:23:58.874
So, I better tell them what can go wrong with doctors

01:23:58.900 --> 01:24:01.757
and what they should be careful about.

01:24:08.775 --> 01:24:13.045
It is to be understood that there is a centre,

01:24:13.094 --> 01:24:17.605
is the second centre which we call as Swadishthan.

01:24:17.619 --> 01:24:19.545
This centre is very interesting.

01:24:19.580 --> 01:24:23.465
It comes out of the Solar Plexus

01:24:23.499 --> 01:24:27.556
we call it a Nabhi Chakra

01:24:27.570 --> 01:24:30.946
and like a lotus and it moves all round you see,

01:24:30.959 --> 01:24:34.826
as you can say in gross way it is Aortic Plexus.

01:24:34.849 --> 01:24:37.028
It supplies energy to Aortic Plexus.

01:24:37.060 --> 01:24:41.516
It is not Aortic Plexus but supplies energy to Aortic Plexus.

01:24:41.527 --> 01:24:46.267
Now this centre is very important

01:24:46.307 --> 01:24:49.128
because it gives energy to our liver,

01:24:49.177 --> 01:24:52.119
to pancreas,

01:24:52.147 --> 01:24:55.689
to our spleen, to our intestines,

01:24:55.704 --> 01:24:56.849
to our kidneys,

01:24:56.854 --> 01:24:59.964
can you imagine such an important centre it is!

01:24:59.951 --> 01:25:01.152
This Swadishthan!

01:25:01.166 --> 01:25:04.262
But the most important work it does is very...

01:25:04.286 --> 01:25:06.612
which I don’t know you will accept or not

01:25:06.646 --> 01:25:10.686
but it supplies energy to our grey cells

01:25:10.701 --> 01:25:13.956
which we are using all the time.

01:25:13.941 --> 01:25:15.924
When we are thinking too much,

01:25:15.931 --> 01:25:19.394
when we are acting physically and mentally,

01:25:19.421 --> 01:25:24.568
this centre has to supply energy to our brain,

01:25:24.561 --> 01:25:28.118
we can call it to our grey cells

01:25:28.142 --> 01:25:31.778
which we are using all the time.

01:25:31.811 --> 01:25:33.118
When we are doctors,

01:25:33.146 --> 01:25:35.426
we are using our grey cells how much?

01:25:35.439 --> 01:25:36.159
We have no idea.

01:25:36.166 --> 01:25:38.882
There is nobody who has found out

01:25:38.916 --> 01:25:40.685
how much we use our brains,

01:25:40.756 --> 01:25:45.718
but we are going exhausting our brains and also, we are very futuristic.

01:25:45.720 --> 01:25:47.888
All doctors are futuristic.

01:25:47.911 --> 01:25:52.632
Maybe they want to find out something

01:25:52.692 --> 01:25:54.753
in the pure sense of the word

01:25:54.770 --> 01:25:57.363
or maybe they have certain ideas

01:25:57.384 --> 01:25:59.170
or maybe it is money,

01:25:59.181 --> 01:26:02.190
may be anything but they are very, very futuristic

01:26:02.201 --> 01:26:05.863
and in that trend of futuristic behaviour also

01:26:05.892 --> 01:26:07.728
there is a big competition

01:26:07.742 --> 01:26:09.448
so they don’t know what to do.

01:26:09.474 --> 01:26:13.018
They have to be futuristic and think but what will happen.

01:26:13.028 --> 01:26:20.497
Now in this kind of movement of the mind

01:26:20.512 --> 01:26:21.310
what happens

01:26:21.340 --> 01:26:23.899
we start becoming very right sided,

01:26:23.897 --> 01:26:25.489
extremely right sided.

01:26:25.517 --> 01:26:27.289
Now as a result of that,

01:26:27.295 --> 01:26:29.545
as a right sided man, you know

01:26:29.565 --> 01:26:31.834
I would say what medically can happen,

01:26:31.854 --> 01:26:35.559
of course also happens lot of things mentally also.

01:26:35.574 --> 01:26:40.205
But what can happen medically,

01:26:40.214 --> 01:26:42.175
this Swadishthan Chakra

01:26:42.224 --> 01:26:44.264
which has to supply to your liver.

01:26:44.275 --> 01:26:45.974
Why do you call it ‘liver’?

01:26:45.994 --> 01:26:47.805
Because of liver we live.

01:26:47.805 --> 01:26:51.926
Liver is very important in Sahaja Yoga.

01:26:51.972 --> 01:26:55.166
I know that in medicine we don’t know much about liver

01:26:55.171 --> 01:26:59.725
and it is absolutely curable in Sahaja Yoga.

01:26:59.732 --> 01:27:01.166
But now what happens,

01:27:01.195 --> 01:27:06.634
liver is the one which takes all the poison of the body

01:27:06.652 --> 01:27:11.191
and throws it into the circulation.

01:27:11.205 --> 01:27:13.744
That everyone knows, all right!

01:27:13.752 --> 01:27:18.272
Now when liver is looked after it is normal,

01:27:18.281 --> 01:27:20.451
then we have also a pancreas,

01:27:20.482 --> 01:27:23.112
then we have spleen

01:27:23.161 --> 01:27:25.181
and also kidneys

01:27:25.216 --> 01:27:28.392
and the last part of intestines,

01:27:28.441 --> 01:27:31.757
intestines as a whole but the last part is very important.

01:27:31.778 --> 01:27:34.538
So, such a man who is always thinking

01:27:34.589 --> 01:27:37.817
all his energy is going to his brain

01:27:37.829 --> 01:27:40.209
and all these organs are neglected

01:27:40.278 --> 01:27:43.663
and he can be affected by any one of them

01:27:43.666 --> 01:27:47.523
So, the first thing he is affected is bad liver.

01:27:47.546 --> 01:27:49.329
Now this bad liver

01:27:49.344 --> 01:27:53.498
because it cannot throw its heat,

01:27:53.523 --> 01:27:55.547
which is the poison of the body

01:27:55.557 --> 01:27:56.858
into the circulation.

01:27:56.907 --> 01:28:00.057
What happens that it starts, heat starts rising,

01:28:00.088 --> 01:28:03.588
this heat goes higher on the right side.

01:28:03.647 --> 01:28:05.318
We call it Right Heart

01:28:05.297 --> 01:28:08.778
which is the centre which controls the lungs.

01:28:08.758 --> 01:28:11.718
So, such a person can get Asthma.

01:28:11.735 --> 01:28:14.428
Now Asthma has been cured through Sahaja Yoga,

01:28:14.455 --> 01:28:16.018
very simple way.

01:28:16.089 --> 01:28:17.625
But it can be cured,

01:28:17.638 --> 01:28:23.215
it gets Asthma. We say it is incurable because we don't know about Swadishthan.

01:28:23.238 --> 01:28:26.985
Now this same thing happens to our…

01:28:27.056 --> 01:28:30.017
when it moves to the left side pancreas.

01:28:30.046 --> 01:28:32.447
Mostly people who are sitting on their chairs

