But how do they know?

01:44:00.513 --> 01:44:02.973
Because on the fingertip they know,

01:44:02.989 --> 01:44:04.543
they show the finger.

01:44:04.592 --> 01:44:07.102
So, everybody will say the same thing,

01:44:07.152 --> 01:44:09.313
because it is Absolute.

01:44:09.382 --> 01:44:10.856
This All-pervading Power

01:44:10.852 --> 01:44:12.826
about which people have talked about,

01:44:12.842 --> 01:44:14.496
they have called it Brahma Chaitanya

01:44:14.502 --> 01:44:16.437
They have called it all kinds of things

01:44:16.441 --> 01:44:19.026
but they don’t know what it is.

01:44:19.026 --> 01:44:23.321
It is this power that starts flowing

01:44:23.322 --> 01:44:25.250
and when it starts flowing through you,

01:44:25.250 --> 01:44:27.420
tremendous things happen,

01:44:27.420 --> 01:44:30.271
tremendous things happen.

01:44:30.291 --> 01:44:31.992
I have known so many bureaucrats

01:44:31.990 --> 01:44:33.762
you see, were so much worried, upset;

01:44:33.792 --> 01:44:36.262
because they were honest people and were suffering.

01:44:36.292 --> 01:44:37.292
They took to Sahaja Yoga.

01:44:37.302 --> 01:44:40.151
Their lives are changed now, they are enjoying themselves.

01:44:40.141 --> 01:44:41.671
They are not bothered.

01:44:41.671 --> 01:44:45.015
Because this not only guides you,

01:44:45.012 --> 01:44:46.685
this not only gives you knowledge

01:44:46.688 --> 01:44:48.904
but also protects you all the time.

01:44:48.908 --> 01:44:50.127
I have seen many doctors

01:44:50.128 --> 01:44:52.256
who are doing say heart trouble.

01:44:52.267 --> 01:44:55.346
Heart patients they are looking after.

01:44:55.362 --> 01:44:58.273
There are doctors who are curing cancer patients

01:44:58.303 --> 01:45:03.092
I met one doctor who has a dialysis hospital;

01:45:03.152 --> 01:45:07.410
but his kidneys.

01:45:07.459 --> 01:45:10.206
I said, “Doctor, how have you got this?”

01:45:10.199 --> 01:45:14.926
So, he is just treating only people for dialysis and he gets his kidneys

01:45:14.949 --> 01:45:17.656
So, there is no protection.

01:45:17.667 --> 01:45:21.247
You should also have the protection as a surgeon has.

01:45:21.279 --> 01:45:23.330
He will tie up his hands and everything.

01:45:23.380 --> 01:45:27.567
But then otherwise normally doctors have no protection of any kind

01:45:27.595 --> 01:45:29.555
when they treat another person

01:45:29.575 --> 01:45:31.025
and if they are sensitive,

01:45:31.085 --> 01:45:34.121
they may catch from them slowly, slowly the diseases,

01:45:34.146 --> 01:45:35.971
which they are going to cure.

01:45:36.003 --> 01:45:39.102
This is also a point nobody thinks of.

01:45:39.099 --> 01:45:41.812
We are not machines, we are human beings,

01:45:41.808 --> 01:45:46.283
we are not a stone, but we are sensitive

01:45:46.301 --> 01:45:48.862
and when you see somebody suffering

01:45:48.871 --> 01:45:51.587
you catch from them.

01:45:51.611 --> 01:45:52.862
You definitely catch

01:45:52.878 --> 01:45:55.320
but in Sahaja Yoga you know you are catching.

01:45:55.347 --> 01:45:58.020
In Sahaja Yoga you know what you are catching

01:45:58.040 --> 01:46:02.340
and you know how to clear it out and how to protect yourself.

01:46:02.410 --> 01:46:04.910
Now this is what one doesn’t understand

01:46:04.969 --> 01:46:08.407
that all human beings can get their Self-realisation,

01:46:08.419 --> 01:46:09.487
all of them.

01:46:09.514 --> 01:46:12.643
Only thing if you are thinking

01:46:12.653 --> 01:46:15.677
that you are a great scientist

01:46:15.694 --> 01:46:19.418
and you are above everything and you have read everything,

01:46:19.444 --> 01:46:21.392
“I don’t have to know anything”,

01:46:21.408 --> 01:46:23.172
then it doesn’t work.

01:46:23.188 --> 01:46:24.563
It cannot force.

01:46:24.567 --> 01:46:27.682
Sahaja Yoga cannot force on you its knowledge, nothing.

01:46:27.717 --> 01:46:31.341
It respects you, and respects your freedom.

01:46:31.355 --> 01:46:32.865
Freedom has been given to you

01:46:32.896 --> 01:46:36.396
whether you take to it or don’t take to it, is your own.

01:46:36.396 --> 01:46:41.385
But if you want it, if you are really desirous of getting it

01:46:41.392 --> 01:46:43.355
then you get it.

01:46:43.362 --> 01:46:45.073
But with that you get knowledge

01:46:45.132 --> 01:46:47.115
not only about medical science

01:46:47.102 --> 01:46:49.536
but also about people.

01:46:49.580 --> 01:46:54.835
Now there are so many types of God men coming.

01:46:54.849 --> 01:46:57.308
Now how will you know they are not correct?

01:46:57.324 --> 01:46:59.324
How will you?

01:46:59.364 --> 01:47:03.505
How will you know that Guru Nanaka was a great,

01:47:03.495 --> 01:47:06.265
not only saint but an incarnation?

01:47:06.265 --> 01:47:07.757
How will you know about Christ?

01:47:07.807 --> 01:47:10.458
How will you know about anyone of them

01:47:10.467 --> 01:47:12.257
because you don’t know the Absolute?

01:47:12.277 --> 01:47:13.635
You are born like that,

01:47:13.648 --> 01:47:15.448
but once you are born in Sahaja Yoga,

01:47:15.497 --> 01:47:16.987
you become a Yogi.

01:47:17.037 --> 01:47:20.523
And then you know exactly that they are all one.

01:47:20.525 --> 01:47:22.083
All the Sufis are one,

01:47:22.084 --> 01:47:24.793
all these great Prophets are one.

01:47:24.823 --> 01:47:29.752
All these we can call them Prophets

01:47:29.765 --> 01:47:31.792
and also incarnations,

01:47:31.798 --> 01:47:34.121
they're altogether one.

01:47:34.099 --> 01:47:35.679
Christ himself has said,

01:47:35.748 --> 01:47:37.948
“Those who are not against us are with us.”

01:47:37.998 --> 01:47:40.360
But how many Christians understand this?

01:47:40.389 --> 01:47:43.070
So, there is no need to have different, different religions.

01:47:43.074 --> 01:47:46.854
It’s in one big huge ocean of knowledge

01:47:46.904 --> 01:47:51.124
which has different, different, we can say, ports

01:47:51.175 --> 01:47:53.932
but that doesn’t mean the ocean is different.

01:47:53.932 --> 01:47:55.928
All your problems will be solved

01:47:56.007 --> 01:47:59.898
as far as integration of religions are concerned

01:47:59.918 --> 01:48:02.348
and you don’t have to give up anything

01:48:02.350 --> 01:48:03.948
but respect everything

01:48:03.949 --> 01:48:08.577
in the right manner that you know about them.

01:48:08.585 --> 01:48:10.345
There is nothing to discard,

01:48:10.416 --> 01:48:12.998
nothing to condemn

01:48:13.015 --> 01:48:15.896
but you just, to know about them,

01:48:15.906 --> 01:48:17.942
then you are amazed

01:48:17.962 --> 01:48:21.185
how they are talking the same thing what you are talking.

01:48:21.192 --> 01:48:23.045
I have read a book

01:48:23.045 --> 01:48:27.925
written by a one great Sufi from Turkey

01:48:27.937 --> 01:48:32.822
and another I have read it with our Nisamuddin

01:48:32.846 --> 01:48:35.842
here who had written something

01:48:35.877 --> 01:48:38.292
and his disciples, just the same,

01:48:38.285 --> 01:48:40.132
they write the same thing.

01:48:40.134 --> 01:48:41.957
I mean there is no difference

01:48:41.977 --> 01:48:44.124
because absolute knowledge is the same,

01:48:44.154 --> 01:48:46.044
only expression may be different.

01:48:46.114 --> 01:48:48.775
They might use different expressions.

01:48:48.834 --> 01:48:52.757
So, you get out of this madness of religion also.

01:48:52.757 --> 01:48:55.439
Religion can never teach you to hate anyone,

01:48:55.448 --> 01:48:56.319
can never,

01:48:56.378 --> 01:49:00.879
because I am talking here about the power of love.

01:49:00.909 --> 01:49:04.527
This All-pervading Power is the power of love.

01:49:04.537 --> 01:49:05.547
It guides you;

01:49:05.567 --> 01:49:06.817
it looks after you,

01:49:06.868 --> 01:49:09.303
it cooperates, it coordinates.

01:49:09.323 --> 01:49:12.023
It is so efficient a government

01:49:12.052 --> 01:49:16.808
that I don’t think we can ever imagine how efficient it is

01:49:16.832 --> 01:49:19.148
and it works just like this.

01:49:19.168 --> 01:49:21.007
Sometimes it is very amazing

01:49:21.027 --> 01:49:23.688
I will tell you now, today a case of a lady

01:49:23.777 --> 01:49:27.503
which is a true case. Is she here now?

01:49:27.507 --> 01:49:29.112
Mexican, no?

01:49:29.122 --> 01:49:30.783
She might be here

01:49:30.793 --> 01:49:32.981
See, there's a lady. You are there!

01:49:32.983 --> 01:49:34.551
She is a lady here.

01:49:34.573 --> 01:49:38.486
She was working with the UN and when I went to New York, she got her Realisation

01:49:38.545 --> 01:49:42.446
and she became a very ardent Sahaja Yogi.

01:49:42.455 --> 01:49:45.415
It rose to that thing where we call shraddha.

01:49:49.556 --> 01:49:52.181
Then she wrote to me three letters

01:49:52.241 --> 01:49:56.926
telling me about some disease her son has got

01:49:56.995 --> 01:50:01.216
who is only eighteen years of age studying in Harvard University or something.

01:50:01.315 --> 01:50:05.943
She said, “Mother this disease some people get it in my family at old age and they die.”

01:50:05.964 --> 01:50:07.935
” It’s a special Mexican disease,

01:50:07.984 --> 01:50:10.373
it’s a big name as usual you see.

01:50:10.386 --> 01:50:14.647
So, I was thinking what to write to her

01:50:14.645 --> 01:50:16.996
and we’re just paying attention.

01:50:17.056 --> 01:50:20.567
And she said, “Should I bring my child there, what should I do?” and all that.

01:50:20.576 --> 01:50:22.377
And the fourth letter I find

01:50:22.457 --> 01:50:26.828
that the doctors have said that he is completely cured,

01:50:26.837 --> 01:50:28.719
there is nothing in it.

01:50:28.725 --> 01:50:31.261
Just imagine how quick it was.

01:50:33.379 --> 01:50:34.871
I mean, I was amazed.

01:50:34.877 --> 01:50:36.481
There are so many cases like that

01:50:36.496 --> 01:50:38.051
but this is something remarkable.

01:50:38.076 --> 01:50:40.545
Where is Mexico! I was in Pune

01:50:40.636 --> 01:50:44.725
and just see how this Paramchaitanya has done it.

01:50:45.685 --> 01:50:47.935
How it is kind!

01:50:47.995 --> 01:50:52.353
It is the power of love of God which looks after you.

01:50:52.362 --> 01:50:54.092
After all the One who has created us,

01:50:54.082 --> 01:50:57.332
the Creator is going to look after us, isn’t it?

01:50:57.413 --> 01:51:04.991
But we should have also little attention towards finding out what is the truth.

01:51:04.998 --> 01:51:06.801
Don’t accept anything,

01:51:06.808 --> 01:51:09.291
you have to find out the truth first of all

01:51:09.308 --> 01:51:11.277
and everybody has said that

01:51:11.337 --> 01:51:13.872
it is the same thing as everybody has said,

01:51:13.888 --> 01:51:15.678
you should know about yourself.

01:51:16.717 --> 01:51:18.772
Guru Nanaka’s thing I will say:

01:51:18.772 --> 01:51:25.088
Kahe ray Ban khojan Jai, Sada Niwasi Sada Alepa, Tohey sang samai

01:51:25.100 --> 01:51:29.732
Pusp maday jo Bas Basat Hai, Mukur Mahey ras chayi

01:51:29.803 --> 01:51:34.558
Taisai hi Hari basay nirantar, Ghat hi khojo bhai

01:51:34.562 --> 01:51:39.018
Kahay nanak bin aapa chinay, Mitay na bhram ki kai’

01:51:39.058 --> 01:51:42.587
He said you must know yourself. “Know thyself” Christ has said.

01:51:42.678 --> 01:51:44.868
Everybody has said you should know yourself.

01:51:44.928 --> 01:51:46.848
Now what is that knowing yourself?

01:51:46.897 --> 01:51:50.854
That is nothing but you are

01:51:50.893 --> 01:51:53.904
the principle is that the truth is this

01:51:53.973 --> 01:51:57.820
that you are not this body, this mind,

01:51:57.830 --> 01:52:00.180
you are not these emotions,

01:52:00.180 --> 01:52:02.560
you are not this ego,

01:52:02.680 --> 01:52:06.973
you are not these conditionings but you are the pure Spirit.

01:52:06.973 --> 01:52:09.127
All our saints have said that.

01:52:09.147 --> 01:52:11.766
Now we are not on that path.

01:52:11.786 --> 01:52:15.094
We are not looking out for what are we.

01:52:15.096 --> 01:52:16.528
If we are the Spirit,

01:52:16.556 --> 01:52:19.538
then how are we to become the Spirit?

01:52:19.556 --> 01:52:21.838
Now anybody who starts talking like that,

01:52:21.879 --> 01:52:24.368
I mean, I was very much opposed by many people

01:52:24.419 --> 01:52:27.299
because they thought I was just telling lies,

01:52:27.288 --> 01:52:31.555
I am this thing, that thing, but when they got sick, they came to Me.

01:52:31.555 --> 01:52:33.167
That’s not the way.

01:52:33.167 --> 01:52:38.544
The way is to try to know that we do not know the absolute.

01:52:38.556 --> 01:52:40.913
Once you become a little humble about it

01:52:40.906 --> 01:52:42.723
that we don’t know the absolute,

01:52:42.768 --> 01:52:46.018
so the religion and science become one

01:52:46.018 --> 01:52:51.198
because you can explain it scientifically as Dr. U.C. Rai has done

01:52:51.221 --> 01:52:54.721
Scientifically, you can explain what happens.

01:52:54.710 --> 01:52:56.330
Now you don’t have to become

01:52:56.330 --> 01:52:59.603
what you call ‘karm-kandi’, ‘ritualistic’, no need

01:52:59.632 --> 01:53:02.373
There is nothing to be done ritualistically, nothing.

01:53:02.402 --> 01:53:04.364
Once you are really realised,

01:53:04.362 --> 01:53:07.022
you have to do a little meditation everyday,

01:53:07.033 --> 01:53:08.473
in the evening.

01:53:08.482 --> 01:53:14.219
Now what I also would I should say this Paramchaitanya

01:53:14.228 --> 01:53:17.877
that it gave us a chance to have a hospital in Vashi

01:53:17.879 --> 01:53:20.227
and the results are very good in Vashi.

01:53:20.259 --> 01:53:23.047
They never use to charge anything for the outdoor patients

01:53:23.047 --> 01:53:24.350
but they said, “Mother,

01:53:24.346 --> 01:53:25.940
please allow us to take ten Rupees.”

01:53:25.969 --> 01:53:29.069
I said, “All right, take ten Rupees, is all right for everything."

01:53:29.080 --> 01:53:32.569
but the people who are living inside,

01:53:32.589 --> 01:53:34.727
they are also paying little amount;

01:53:34.750 --> 01:53:37.583
nothing compared to what people pay in the hospitals.

01:53:37.596 --> 01:53:41.246
And Dr. Rai has so sacrificingly accepted.

01:53:41.266 --> 01:53:44.022
And the doctors are coming from Russia all the way.

01:53:44.051 --> 01:53:47.062
You know, Russian doctors are wonderful doctors.

01:53:47.082 --> 01:53:49.911
They are very great scientists, I must say.

01:53:49.982 --> 01:53:56.100
They have gone very far in scientific approach.

01:53:56.150 --> 01:53:58.824
They have tried to find out the energies,

01:53:58.861 --> 01:54:00.111
which are subtle energies,

01:54:00.120 --> 01:54:01.699
and lots of things they have done,

01:54:01.710 --> 01:54:03.560
but specially, they are very much interested

01:54:03.631 --> 01:54:08.388
in working through Sahaja Yoga and they are coming down here to work.

01:54:08.391 --> 01:54:12.678
Now I would not expect our doctors to come and work like that,

01:54:12.690 --> 01:54:15.178
but at least for once a week,

01:54:15.190 --> 01:54:16.868
they can give some time

01:54:16.890 --> 01:54:23.333
and they can practice Sahaja Yoga just as a blessing to the people.

01:54:23.335 --> 01:54:25.736
Our country is full of very poor people,

01:54:25.745 --> 01:54:28.665
very, very poor people, extremely poor

01:54:28.676 --> 01:54:31.065
and we feel very much concerned.

01:54:31.096 --> 01:54:32.273
People always ask Me,

01:54:32.277 --> 01:54:34.243
“Yours is such a Yoga Bhoomi

01:54:34.257 --> 01:54:36.087
then, the, why the people are poor?

01:54:36.116 --> 01:54:37.357
The poor they are,

01:54:37.366 --> 01:54:41.022
because they do not follow the right path.

01:54:41.016 --> 01:54:43.223
You see, if they follow the right path,

01:54:43.246 --> 01:54:45.705
Lakshmi is also there to bless you.

01:54:45.743 --> 01:54:47.565
There is nothing to worry about money,

01:54:47.582 --> 01:54:49.300
nothing to worry about anything

01:54:49.306 --> 01:54:55.150
and you become a person who is absolutely in balance.

01:54:55.156 --> 01:54:57.815
As soon as something comes up,

01:54:57.835 --> 01:54:59.266
some crisis come up,

01:54:59.274 --> 01:55:01.875
immediately you all become silent

01:55:01.946 --> 01:55:04.966
and you start seeing what’s wrong,

01:55:04.975 --> 01:55:06.346
what is the problem.

01:55:06.366 --> 01:55:08.276
Because you are not silent,

01:55:08.299 --> 01:55:09.426
always in the conflict,

01:55:09.439 --> 01:55:11.376
you cannot see the problem clearly

01:55:11.399 --> 01:55:13.376
and you cannot solve it,

01:55:13.379 --> 01:55:17.178
but, you actually, you don’t solve any problem.

01:55:17.199 --> 01:55:19.549
It is this, I must say this power.

01:55:19.618 --> 01:55:22.723
I also tell them I don’t do anything; I am just sitting down;

01:55:22.723 --> 01:55:24.068
this power is doing everything.

01:55:24.064 --> 01:55:25.218
They don’t believe it

01:55:25.223 --> 01:55:26.638
but it is a fact.

01:55:26.634 --> 01:55:28.338
I am not doing anything, I am just sitting,

01:55:28.353 --> 01:55:31.438
I am not planning, I am not doing anything whatsoever

01:55:31.449 --> 01:55:33.529
but this power does everything for us

01:55:33.578 --> 01:55:34.748
so why should I do it.

01:55:34.819 --> 01:55:39.060
But, it’s rather difficult for human beings to leave things to this power.

01:55:39.078 --> 01:55:42.540
Even some doctors, who have been practising Medical Science

01:55:42.558 --> 01:55:46.379
have had very funny experiences

01:55:46.390 --> 01:55:49.060
Like there’s one Dr. Amjad Ali in Australia

01:55:49.080 --> 01:55:51.017
who is very well qualified

01:55:51.011 --> 01:55:53.827
and he was experimenting

01:55:53.830 --> 01:55:57.261
on some sort of “kya kar rahe they.”

01:56:00.779 --> 01:56:03.221
So, you see that what he found

01:56:03.301 --> 01:56:07.362
when he went close to them, they start becoming smaller.

01:56:07.370 --> 01:56:08.542
He could not experiment.

01:56:08.547 --> 01:56:10.902
He said, “How my experiment will go?

01:56:10.937 --> 01:56:14.487
Because I cannot! As soon as I go near them, everything disappears,

01:56:14.487 --> 01:56:15.694
all the disease disappears,

01:56:15.717 --> 01:56:16.674
so what can I do?”

01:56:16.678 --> 01:56:18.774
I said, “You don’t experiment with that

01:56:18.783 --> 01:56:23.694
but you can experiment with the people who are already sick and do something about it.”

01:56:23.674 --> 01:56:25.163
So, there are many things like that.

01:56:25.163 --> 01:56:27.265
And another person told me that in England

01:56:27.263 --> 01:56:29.634
there is a craze for research.

01:56:29.674 --> 01:56:35.183
So, one scientist, they told him, “You find out what is minus 273,

01:56:35.243 --> 01:56:36.574
the absolute zero.

01:56:36.643 --> 01:56:41.941
So, he said, “I cannot, because the formula is such that some heat will remain always there.”

01:56:41.942 --> 01:56:42.961
I said, “All right,

01:56:42.958 --> 01:56:44.591
do one thing,

01:56:44.598 --> 01:56:48.158
you go and tell them this is absolute and how can we find absolute.”

01:56:48.174 --> 01:56:49.955
“We cannot find Absolute.

01:56:49.989 --> 01:56:53.346
It is absolutely, absolutely beyond us”.

01:56:53.355 --> 01:56:57.025
Then I said, “You use vibrations and you use these Divine vibrations.”

01:56:57.038 --> 01:57:00.091
And he achieved it. He got his doctorate and he did it.

01:57:00.098 --> 01:57:01.632
So, they asked him, “How did you do it?”

01:57:01.641 --> 01:57:03.422
He said, “I cannot explain to you.”

01:57:03.420 --> 01:57:04.792
“Because if I talk to them,

01:57:04.810 --> 01:57:06.111
they will never listen to me.

01:57:06.120 --> 01:57:08.493
These scientists, you know, they think no end of themselves.

01:57:08.511 --> 01:57:11.592
How can I tell them that I did it with this Divine Power?”

01:57:11.607 --> 01:57:14.210
They cannot believe that there is another big power

01:57:14.230 --> 01:57:16.109
After all who runs our heart?

